H0.text: Adult → pupa → larva → egg is the sequence that shows the life cycle of some insects.

H1.text: Egg -> pupa -> larva -> adult is the sequence that shows the life cycle of some insects.

H2.text: Larva → pupa → egg → adult is a sequence that shows the life cycle of some insects.

H3.text: Egg → larva → pupa → adult is the sequence that shows the life cycle of some insects.

A4.text: Holometabolous insects pass through a larval stage, then enter a pupal stage, and finally emerge as adults.

A5.text: In holometabolous insects, immature stages are called larvae, which then enter an inactive pupal stage before emerging as adults.
